      <description>&lt;p&gt;Try to make a nixos boot animation. (log scroll on screen.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The repo link: &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ocfox/booti&#34;&gt;https://github.com/ocfox/booti&lt;/a&gt; . This site has none imported js or css library.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First need make a animation let text display line by line.
So I tried to set a delay for every line, when open page hide (don&amp;rsquo;t display) every paragraph in css.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#abb2bf;background-color:#282c34;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-css&#34; data-lang=&#34;css&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e06c75&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#c678dd&#34;&gt;display&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e5c07b&#34;&gt;none&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#7f848e&#34;&gt;/* Initially hide all paragraphs */&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#c678dd&#34;&gt;margin&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d19a66&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e5c07b&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d19a66&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d19a66&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d19a66&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e5c07b&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Then set a delay increase by degrees for every single line with js. Use &lt;code&gt;EventListener&lt;/code&gt; get every
paragraph element, and set 500ms * (current lines) delay make it &lt;code&gt;display&lt;/code&gt; &lt;code&gt;none&lt;/code&gt; -&amp;gt; &lt;code&gt;block&lt;/code&gt;.
So them will display right.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
